Check whether a given String S is a palindrome using recursion. Return true or false.
Input Format :
String S
Output Format :
'true' or 'false'
Constraints :
0 <= |S| <= 1000
where |S| represents length of string S.
Sample Input 1 :
racecar
Sample Output 1:
true
Sample Input 2 :
ninja
Sample Output 2:
false

Your Code
C++ (g++ 5.4)
1234567891011121314
bool check(char input[],int n){
    if(n<=1)
        return true;
    if(input[0]==input[n-1])
        return check(input+1,n-2);
    return false;
}

